          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true">A new </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text HowTo" translate="true"> is now at the end of the motion, </text><text styleclass="HowTo Numbered" style="font-weight:normal;" translate="true">after the last </text><text styleclass="Element" translate="true">segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">. </text></para>
          <para styleclass="Body Text HowTo"><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">The new segment is now the </text><text styleclass="Element-Header" translate="true">Selected-Segment</text><text styleclass="Body Text" translate="true">.</text></para>
